# Metrics & monitoring — live rates and sparklines (global key: ctrl+t)
Output vhs/gifs/metrics-and-monitoring.gif
Source vhs/_config.tape

Hide
Type "./kafui --mock" Enter
Sleep 3s
Show

Sleep 1500ms
# Open the metrics page; let a couple of collection cycles fill the sparklines
Ctrl+T
Sleep 5s
Down@450ms 3
Sleep 2s

Hide
Ctrl+C
